125
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:07,920
Seems like they have at least a little bit of a portfolio

126
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:12,860
Such that I can tell if the style would mesh well with whatever topic from the domain expert I end up finding

127
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:15,700
And then I would be there as a kind of producer and extra collaborator

128
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:18,760
And we could post the final product on 3Blue1Brown

